title: doing your own thing & not giving a f*%k
itunes:title: doing your own thing & not giving a f*%k
description:
Brooke and Danielle are joined by RGR aka Rish to discuss her crazy life!  Rish moved to NYC while taking a gap semester from UC Berkley to pursue fashion.  She works 2 jobs while managing dating, meeting new people, and adulting at the age of 20!  The gals also discuss the results of the election and share some insights from the past week.

LifeofRGR Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lifeofrgr/
